model.haskell_template:
import Control.Applicative
import Control.Monad
import System.IO


main :: IO ()
main = do
    a_temp <- getLine
    let a_t = words a_temp
    let a = read $ a_t!!0 :: Int
    let b = read $ a_t!!1 :: Int
    let c = read $ a_t!!2 :: Int
    let d = read $ a_t!!3 :: Int

getMultipleLines :: Int -> IO [String]

getMultipleLines n
    | n <= 0 = return []
    | otherwise = do          
        x <- getLine         
        xs <- getMultipleLines (n-1)    
        let ret = (x:xs)    
        return ret

model.erlang_template:
-module(solution).

main() ->

    { ok, [A,B,C,D]} = io:fread("", "~d~d~d~d"),
    true.

read_array(0,D) -> [];
read_array(N,D) -> 
	{ok, [X]} = io:fread("", D),
	[X | read_array(N-1,D)].

read_2darray(0,M,D) -> [];
read_2darray(N,M,D) ->
	Q=read_array(M,D),
	[Q | read_2darray(N-1,M,D)].
